  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single Player Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn drift points and make money</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden bonuses across the city</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock drift achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience different physics modes (Tarmac & Snow)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with friends or drivers from around the world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the city map together</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete to achieve the best drift scores</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Menu & Garage</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase new cars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade and customize your vehicles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy parts from the store</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Store up to 100 parts in your inventory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Install or sell any part</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean and optimized graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth and optimized performance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic car sounds (blow-off, exhaust, backfires, tire skids, etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic driving physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic camera system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steering wheel support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fuel system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tire wear system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engine wear and repair system</p></li></ul>",
